    • Method Detail

      • step

        public void step()
          throws NoRouteFoundException
        Moves one step through the maze and updates the images. If along the path an image cannot be resolved the application meets a fatal error and it cannot proceed. This can only happen during abnormal loading.
        Throws:
        NoRouteFoundException - If the maze is unsolvable
